href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2532761\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2532761\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 08, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104unf1665702578355.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/unf1665702578355.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/unf1665702578355.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"unf1665702578355\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"unf1665702578355__repeat_235462\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Define a <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">repeat</span>/<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">until</span> loop.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"unf1665702578355__p_d76229e1_d76230e1_d76231e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">repeat</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"unf1665702578355__p_d76232e1_d76233e1_d76234e1\">... <var class=\"keyword varname\">one or more ProcScript instructions</var> ...</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"unf1665702578355__p_d76235e1_d76236e1_d76237e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">until</span> (<var class=\"keyword varname\">Condition</var>)</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"unf1665702578355__topic_d50082e1_d50083e1_d50084e1_d50085e1_d50086e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d688735e83\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"unf1665702578355__d6071e20\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"unf1665702578355__d6071e20__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"unf1665702578355__d6071e20__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"unf1665702578355__d6071e20__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"unf1665702578355__d6071e20__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Condition</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"unf1665702578355__d6071e20__entry__2\">\n Boolean\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"unf1665702578355__d6071e20__entry__3\">Boolean expression that must evaluate to\n                           <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">TRUE</span> before the repeat loop can end. Uniface converts\n                        any data types specified in the expression to boolean data types. For more\n                        information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hju1665702578520.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hju1665702578520.html\" title=\"When assigning, comparing, and evaluating data in variables, fields, parameters, and expressions, it is possible for mismatches in data type to occur. In such cases, Uniface does not generate an error, but implicitly converts the data type from its source type to the target type.\">Type Conversion</a>.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"unf1665702578355__topic_d50087e1_d50088e1_d50089e1_d50090e1_d50091e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d688735e148\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"unf1665702578355__p_d76244e1_d76245e1_d76246e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">repeat</span> statement does not affect <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"unf1665702578355__topic_d50092e1_d50093e1_d50094e1_d50095e1_d50096e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d688735e163\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"unf1665702578355__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"unf1665702578355__topic_d50097e1_d50098e1_d50099e1_d50100e1_d50101e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d688735e172\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"unf1665702578355__p_d76256e1_d76257e1_d76258e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">repeat</span> statement loops through the ProcScript statements that follow it until the <var class=\"keyword varname\">Condition</var> on the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">until</span> clause is evaluated as <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">TRUE</span> (that is, nonzero). Uniface then leaves the loop and continues with the statement following the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">until</span> clause (if any).</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"unf1665702578355__p_d76259e1_d76260e1_d76261e1\">Use the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">break</span> statement to terminate a <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">repeat</span>/<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">until</span> loop early.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"unf1665702578355__p_d76262e1_d76263e1_d76264e1\">Conditional statements such as <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">if</span>/<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">endif</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">while</span>/<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">endwhile</span>, and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">repeat</span>/<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">until</span> can be nested up to 32 levels. It can be useful to indent all statements between the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">repeat</span> and corresponding <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">until</span>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"unf1665702578355__section_gvh_vsl_zbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d688735e236\">Example: Repeat/Until Loop </h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following example shows the use of the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">repeat</span>\n            statement. The example loops through all the occurrences of entity E1, until it finds an\n            occurrence where the values of the fields F2 and NAMEDUMMY are the same, or until all\n            the occurrences have been checked.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"unf1665702578355__pre_myv_vsl_zbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">; F2.E1 is a character string field containing a name\n; loop until field matches or setocc is out of occurrences\n; field: NAMEDUMMY.E1\n\nif (F2.E1 != NAMEDUMMY)\n vCurrOcc = $curocc\n $NAME$ = NAMEDUMMY\n i = 1\n repeat\n setocc \"E1\", i\n i = (i + 1)\n until ((f2.E1 = $NAME$) | ($status &lt; 0))\n if ($status &lt; 0)\n message \"%%$NAME$%%% is not available.\"\n setocc \"E1\", vCurrOcc\n return (-1)\n endif\nendif\n$prompt = F2.E1\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wrg1665702578278.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>break</a><p>Unconditionally exit a loop initiated by for, forentity, forlist, repeat, or while.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nzz1707817327409.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>selectcase</a><p>Define a block of conditional case selections.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/byf1707816568807.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Conditions</a><p>A condition is a logical expression that evaluates to a boolean value. It is typically used in conditional processing initiated by ProcScript statements such as if, repeat, selectcase, and while.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jbm1707818341035.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Operators</a><p>Operators perform arithmetic, relational, logical, string manipulation, struct member de-reference, operation de-reference, and field indirection operations in ProcScript instructions.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532761\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532761\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "repeat Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 08, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Define a repeat / until loop. repeat ... one or more ProcScript instructions ... until ( Condition ) Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description Condition Boolean Boolean expression that must evaluate to TRUE before the repeat loop can end. Uniface converts any data types specified in the expression to boolean data types. For more information, see Type Conversion . Return Values The repeat statement does not affect $status . Use Allowed in all component types. Description The repeat statement loops through the ProcScript statements that follow it until the Condition on the until clause is evaluated as TRUE (that is, nonzero). Uniface then leaves the loop and continues with the statement following the until clause (if any). Use the break statement to terminate a repeat / until loop early. Conditional statements such as if / endif , while / endwhile , and repeat / until can be nested up to 32 levels. It can be useful to indent all statements between the repeat and corresponding until . Example: Repeat/Until Loop The following example shows the use of the repeat statement. The example loops through all the occurrences of entity E1, until it finds an occurrence where the values of the fields F2 and NAMEDUMMY are the same, or until all the occurrences have been checked. ; F2.E1 is a character string field containing a name ; loop until field matches or setocc is out of occurrences ; field: NAMEDUMMY.E1 if (F2.E1 != NAMEDUMMY) vCurrOcc = $curocc $NAME$ = NAMEDUMMY i = 1 repeat setocc \"E1\", i i = (i + 1) until ((f2.E1 = $NAME$) | ($status < 0)) if ($status < 0) message \"%%$NAME$%%% is not available.\" setocc \"E1\", vCurrOcc return (-1) endif endif $prompt = F2.E1 Copy Related Links break Unconditionally exit a loop initiated by for, forentity, forlist, repeat, or while. selectcase Define a block of conditional case selections. Conditions A condition is a logical expression that evaluates to a boolean value. It is typically used in conditional processing initiated by ProcScript statements such as if, repeat, selectcase, and while. Operators Operators perform arithmetic, relational, logical, string manipulation, struct member de-reference, operation de-reference, and field indirection operations in ProcScript instructions. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}